        <abstract>
            <p>Describes the flower and mode of action of a particular orchid.</p> 
<p>Has been examining <hi rend="italic">Spiranthes</hi> and is experimenting to see whether insects are necessary for its fertilisation.</p>  
<p>It seems that <hi rend="italic">Oncidium</hi> is designed so as <hi rend="italic">not</hi> to be fertilised.</p> 
        </abstract>
